cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of machine learning in wireless communications and specifically focuses on leveraging visual sensory information. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses the use of 3D-modeling and ray-tracing software to generate synthetic data, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of wireless networks (cs.NI) and multimedia (cs.MM) in the context of vision-aided wireless communications.
